commit message: Basic code layout. Still crashes, needs a lot of cleanup
Forgot to add files to the last commit
Docs and changed the graph type. TimeChart does not work for us.
Bugfix: Don't crash when hitting the back button on the readout activity.

Changed the channel colors, replaced green with blue (green is a problematic color, some displays may make it hard to distinguish from yellow and colorblind people would have problems distinguishing it from red).
Put Y axis labels next to the axis instead of on top of it.
Accuracy is already displayed in the title -> no extra textfield needed.
UI Tweak: Switched colors for first and third channel.
Stop sampling when the user pans the display.
Declared SDK version in order to prevent to app from requesting default permissions it does not need.
